<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Penalty Blitz - Support</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: white;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 12%, rgba(255,255,255,0.22), transparent 18%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(5, 20, 45, 0.75), rgba(0, 70, 28, 0.65)),
        repeating-linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          #0f8a3a 0px,
          #0f8a3a 90px,
          #0b7631 90px,
          #0b7631 180px
        );
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background:
        linear-gradient(transparent 0 38%, rgba(255,255,255,0.22) 38% 38.4%, transparent 38.4%),
        linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0 49.8%, rgba(255,255,255,0.18) 49.8% 50.2%, transparent 50.2%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 38%, transparent 0 74px, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 75px 77px, transparent 78px);
      opacity: 0.85;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 42px 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 34px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .icon {
      width: 96px;
      height: 96px;
      margin: 0 auto 18px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 54px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #19c85a, #087332);
      box-shadow: inset 0 3px 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.3), 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 72px);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-shadow: 0 5px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
    }

    .tagline {
      margin-top: 14px;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    }

    .goal {
      position: relative;
      width: min(100%, 440px);
      height: 170px;
      margin: 26px auto 0;
      border: 8px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      border-bottom: none;
      border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
      background:
        repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.18) 0 2px, transparent 2px 22px),
        repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.18) 0 2px, transparent 2px 22px);
    }

    .keeper {
      position: absolute;
      left: 50%;
      bottom: -22px;
      transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-12deg);
      font-size: 54px;
    }

    .ball {
      position: absolute;
      right: 58px;
      top: 52px;
      font-size: 38px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.35));
    }

    section {
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    p, li {
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 22px;
    }

    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    a.button {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 800;
      padding: 13px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    }

    a.button.primary {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #087332;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 26px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .card { padding: 24px; }
      .goal { height: 145px; }
      .keeper { font-size: 46px; }
      .ball { font-size: 32px; right: 38px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="hero">
        <div class="icon">⚽️</div>
        <h1>Penalty Blitz</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Swipe. Shoot. Score. A quick arcade penalty game for iPhone.</p>

        <div class="goal" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="ball">⚽️</div>
          <div class="keeper">🧤</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section>
        <h2>Support</h2>
        <p>
          Need help with Penalty Blitz? For questions, bugs, feedback, or purchase issues,
          contact us by email.
        </p>
        <div class="buttons">
          <a class="button primary" href="mailto:gd.denis@gmail.com?subject=Penalty%20Blitz%20Support">Contact Support</a>
          <a class="button" href="privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>About the game</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Swipe the ball to shoot penalties.</li>
          <li>Beat the goalkeeper and chase your best score.</li>
          <li>Fast, simple, and fun arcade gameplay.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Tips</h2>
        <p>
          Try different swipe angles, aim for the corners, and keep your timing sharp.
          The keeper will not make it easy.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
      © 2026 Penalty Blitz. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
